{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_18","type":"reasoning","text":"**Investigating API Method**\n\nI'm considering how the `load_seasons` function interacts with `c.get_seasons`. It seems like it might accidentally return all episodes, which could be a bug in the API method. If the `get_seasons` endpoint returns all descendant items, that could lead to thousands of items with images, potentially overwhelming memory. I really need to inspect the API client to understand how `get_seasons` is functioning to avoid any issues. I'm on it!"}}
