{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_51","type":"reasoning","text":"**Investigating memory issues**\n\nI’m thinking there might be an out-of-memory issue happening when navigating at home. Every key press could be triggering some preloading, which might lead to a loop around 2753. It’s possible there’s a memory leak. I should inspect around 2700 and look into the callbacks for focus changes and possibly some queues that could be causing this. It's a lot to consider, but I want to get to the bottom of it!"}}
